add

void add(Address a)
add an Address instance to the AddressList

if it does not match any of the existing addresses in the list, it is added to the list

if it matches an entry already in the list, it is added to the duplicates list associated with that entry

Parameters:
a - Address instance to add to the AddressList

print

void print(java.io.PrintWriter out)
print the AddressList to 'out'

it prints out each entry; if that entry has any duplicates, it then prints out the duplicates as commented lines

Parameters:
out - a PrintWriter onto file "MergedAddresses.out"
